The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Aamir

 Mumbai, Feb. 10 (PTI): Superstar Aamir Khan has received a threatening letter from an anonymous person, police said today. 

 Deputy commissioner (Bandra region) Amitabh Gupta said the star received the letter a month ago and informed the police.

 ?The issue does not appear to be serious and we are not investigating the matter,? he said, adding the police had checked the matter thoroughly.

 Asked if there was any underworld element involved, Gupta refused comment. ?I have nothing more to say about the matter.?




